@startuml UC_Diagram_1_System_Overview

title Use Case Diagram 1: System Overview & Authentication

left to right direction

' ============================================
' ACTORS
' ============================================
actor "Cashier" as Cashier <<Primary Actor>>
actor "Worker" as Worker <<Secondary Actor>>
actor "Administration" as Admin <<Secondary Actor>>

' ============================================
' SYSTEM BOUNDARY
' ============================================
rectangle "Chicken Farm Management System - MVP" {
  
  ' ============ AUTHENTICATION ============
  package "Authentication" {
    usecase "Login" as UC1
    usecase "Logout" as UC2
  }
  
  ' ============ DASHBOARD ============
  package "Dashboard" {
    usecase "View Dashboard" as UC3
    usecase "View Total Chickens Count" as UC3.1
    usecase "View Today's Egg Production" as UC3.2
    usecase "View Active Alerts" as UC3.3
    usecase "View 7-Day Production Chart" as UC3.4
  }
  
  ' ============ MAIN MODULES ============
  package "Main Modules" {
    usecase "Manage Livestock & Farm" as UC4
    usecase "Manage Storage & Inventory" as UC5
    usecase "Manage Personnel & Tasks" as UC6
  }
  
  ' ============ REPORTING ============
  package "Reporting" {
    usecase "Generate Reports" as UC7
  }
  
}

' ============================================
' ACTOR RELATIONSHIPS
' ============================================
Cashier --> UC1
Cashier --> UC2
Cashier --> UC3
Cashier --> UC4
Cashier --> UC5
Cashier --> UC6
Cashier --> UC7

' Secondary actors communicate with Cashier
Worker .up.> Cashier : <<provides feedback>>\nmortality reports\negg counts\ntask completion
Admin .down.> Cashier : <<requests reports>>\nfarm status\nproduction data

' ============================================
' USE CASE RELATIONSHIPS
' ============================================

' Dashboard includes (always shown)
UC3 ..> UC3.1 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC3.2 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC3.3 : <<include>>
UC3 ..> UC3.4 : <<include>>

' ============================================
' NOTES
' ============================================
note right of Cashier
  <b>Primary Actor</b>
  The only system user
  
  Responsibilities:
  • Enters all data
  • Manages farm operations
  • Receives worker feedback
  • Provides reports to Admin
end note

note left of Worker
  <b>Secondary Actor</b>
  Does NOT use the app
  
  Provides to Cashier:
  • Task completion status
  • Mortality reports
  • Egg collection counts
  • Feed usage updates
  • Equipment issues
end note

note left of Admin
  <b>Secondary Actor</b>
  Farm Owner/Management
  
  Requests from Cashier:
  • Farm status reports
  • Production statistics
  • Inventory levels
  • Staff performance
end note

@enduml
